bzh.plealog.bioinfo.api.data.searchresult.io

Interface SRLoader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BlastLoader, NativeBlastLoader

    public interface SRLoader
    This interface defines a Blast loader. Such a loader aims at converting a Blast file into an object representation , namely a BOutput.
    Author:
    Patrick G. Durand
